FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779106273
OL,3,CWoman killed in Bristol house
OL,4,Cexplosion died from blast injuries,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FAvon and Somerset Police are treating
OL,8,Fthe cause of the explosion as
OL,9,Fdeliberate, and recorded Ms Shaw's
OL,10,Fdeath as a homicide. The force is not
OL,11,Flooking for anyone else in connection
OL,12,Fwith her death.
OL,14,FThree other people, including a child,
OL,15,Fsustained minor injuries.
OL,17,FAn inquest into her death was opened
OL,18,Fby assistant Avon coroner Debbie
OL,19,FRookes during a brief hearing at Avon
OL,20,FCoroner's Court in Flax Bourton.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779106273
OL,3,CWoman killed in Bristol house
OL,4,Cexplosion died from blast injuries,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FCoroner's officer Abigail Carey told
OL,8,Fthe hearing Ms Shaw was pronounced
OL,9,Fdead at home by paramedics at 7am,
OL,10,Fshortly after the incident.
OL,12,F"Police and emergency services
OL,13,Fattended her home address following
OL,14,Factivation of an explosive device,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
OL,17,F"A short form post-mortem report from
OL,18,FDr Russell Delaney gives a proposed
OL,19,Fcause of death as penetrating
OL,20,Ffragmentation blast injury to the
OL,21,Fchest and pelvis."
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@cO]yD@AOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779106273
OL,3,CWoman killed in Bristol house
OL,4,Cexplosion died from blast injuries,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FThe court heard Ms Shaw, who was
OL,8,Fsingle and who worked as a personal
OL,9,Fassistant, was formally identified by
OL,10,Fher family.
OL,12,FMs Rookes formally adjourned
OL,13,Fproceedings and requested further
OL,14,Freports from a general practitioner,
OL,15,Fthe police, ambulance service and
OL,16,Fpathologist.
OL,18,FShe also requested further background
OL,19,Finformation from Ms Shaw's family, who
OL,20,Fwere not present at the hearing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779106273
OL,3,CWoman killed in Bristol house
OL,4,Cexplosion died from blast injuries,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FAdjourning the hearing, the coroner
OL,8,Fsaid: "The file will be reviewed by a
OL,9,Fcoroner on July 20 and I will
OL,10,Fprovisionally list this matter for an
OL,11,Finquest hearing here at Avon Coroner's
OL,12,FCourt on August 11 2026."
OL,14,FMs Shaw's family said in a tribute:
OL,15,F"Joanne brought warmth, kindness, and
OL,16,Fstrength into the lives of countless
OL,17,Fpeople.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@YO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779106273
OL,3,CWoman killed in Bristol house
OL,4,Cexplosion died from blast injuries,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,F"Her loving presence will be missed
OL,8,Fmore than words can ever express, but
OL,9,Fher memory will forever remain in our
OL,10,Fhearts."
OL,12,FThey added: "Her child has suffered
OL,13,Fthe unimaginable loss of their mummy
OL,14,Fin this tragedy.
OL,16,F"Joanne's love for her child was
OL,17,Fboundless, and the centre of her
OL,18,Fworld. She was a devoted and loving
OL,19,Fmother.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@HO]tD@MOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779106273
OL,3,CWoman killed in Bristol house
OL,4,Cexplosion died from blast injuries,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,F"Joanne's actions were nothing short
OL,8,Fof heroic. She showed extraordinary
OL,9,Fstrength, selflessness, and love in
OL,10,Fthe face of unimaginable fear, placing
OL,11,Fherself between danger and those she
OL,12,Floved.
OL,14,F"She will always be remembered not for
OL,15,Fthe violence inflicted upon her, but
OL,16,Ffor her bravery, her protective
OL,17,Finstinct, and the ultimate sacrifice
OL,18,Fshe made for others.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779106273
OL,3,CWoman killed in Bristol house
OL,4,Cexplosion died from blast injuries,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,F"We ask for privacy at this deeply
OL,8,Fdifficult time as we mourn our tragic
OL,9,Floss. Joanne will always be in our
OL,10,Fmemories, our thoughts, and our hearts.
OL,12,F"We love you forever, sweetheart.
OL,13,FMummy, I miss you and love you so
OL,14,Fmuch."
OL,16,FMs Shaw, known as Jo, grew up in the
OL,17,FStapleton area of Bristol where her
OL,18,Ffamily said she was well-known for her
OL,19,F"bubbly, friendly personality".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@FO]{D@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779106273
OL,3,CWoman killed in Bristol house
OL,4,Cexplosion died from blast injuries,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FThey said she loved meeting new
OL,8,Fpeople, listening to their stories,
OL,9,Fsharing advice and forming connections
OL,10,Fresulting in "eternal friendships".
OL,12,FShe was the "life and soul not only of
OL,13,Fthe party, but our lives", they added.
OL,15,FPolice previously said a call was
OL,16,Freceived from a person inside the
OL,17,Fhouse at 6.17am reporting a domestic-
OL,18,Frelated incident, saying a man they
OL,19,Fknew had forced entry to the house.
OL,26,@rD@NOUrD@bO]tD@MOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779106273
OL,3,CWoman killed in Bristol house
OL,4,Cexplosion died from blast injuries,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FThe caller remained on the line while
OL,8,Fofficers were dispatched to the house,
OL,9,Fand at 6.30am the caller told police
OL,10,Fthe man was believed to be in
OL,11,Fpossession of an explosive device.
OL,13,FAbout two minutes later there was an
OL,14,Fexplosion at the property, in which Ms
OL,15,FShaw and her former partner died.
OL,17,FOfficers arrived at the property at
OL,18,F6.34am and fire and ambulance services
OL,19,Fshortly afterwards.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
