FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779106273
OL,3,CWoman killed in Bristol house
OL,4,Cexplosion died from blast injuries,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FResidents were evacuated from
OL,8,Fneighbouring properties as a
OL,9,Fprecaution, and searches were carried
OL,10,Fout by the Army to ensure the area was
OL,11,Fsafe.
OL,13,FSearches also took place at an address
OL,14,Fin Speedwell where Mr Kelly lived. No
OL,15,Fevacuations were required at that
OL,16,Flocation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
